      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total showstopper! This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered in a climate-controlled garage, so the paint is sparkling and the interior is spotless. It drives like an absolute dream! I'm looking for a smooth, easy sale, so come take a look and see for yourself how perfect this ride is. You won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
